<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BonusPlayersLive</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { background: #050505 url('/caracter/page/welcome.jpg') no-repeat center center fixed; background-size: cover; color: white; }
        .glass-box { background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border-radius: 20px; padding: 25px; height: 100%; }
        .neon-text { color: #39FF14; text-shadow: 0 0 10px #39FF14; }
        .form-overlay { display: none; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.85); z-index: 2000; justify-content: center; align-items: center; }
        .auth-card { background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6); border: 1px solid #39FF14; padding: 30px; border-radius: 20px; width: 350px; }
        .btn-revolution { background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff003c, #39FF14); color: white; border: none; padding: 15px 40px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 900; animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
        @keyframes pulse { 0% { transform: scale(1); } 50% { transform: scale(1.05); } 100% { transform: scale(1); } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h1 class="display-3 neon-text fw-bold">BonusPlayersLive</h1>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3 mt-3">
                <button class="btn btn-outline-info" onclick="showAuth('login')">LOGIN</button>
                <button class="btn btn-success" onclick="showAuth('register')">REGISTER</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="glass-box">
                    <h4 class="neon-text">BLOK 1: VR VİZYONU</h4>
                    <p>V3 hedefimiz VR gözlükle oynanabilen, hayal gücünü zorlayan gerçekçi bir oyun dünyasıdır. 2026'da bu hedefe ulaşacağız.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="glass-box">
                    <h4 class="neon-text">BLOK 2: EKONOMİ</h4>
                    <p>%75 Şirket, %15 Borsa, %5 Oyun, %5 Reklam. Kayıtta 2500 BPL hediye! BEP20 cüzdanınıza transfer imkanı.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="glass-box">
                    <h4 class="neon-text">BLOK 3: 2028 SAĞLIK</h4>
                    <p>Kanser araştırmaları ve hammadde tedariği ile sağlık sektöründe devrim yaratacağız. Üniversite protokollerimiz yolda.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-5">
            <div class="p-4 glass-box border-info">
                <h3 class="text-info">OUR PROMISE</h3>
                <p class="lead">"Our potential, expertise, and dedicated team go beyond our promises. With your support, we will achieve even more."</p>
                <button class="btn-revolution" onclick="showAuth('register')">JOIN THE REVOLUTION</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="form-overlay" id="authOverlay">
        <div class="auth-card">
            <h3 class="text-center mb-4">ACCESS PANEL</h3>
            <form id="authForm" method="POST">
                <input type="email" name="email" class="form-control mb-3 bg-dark text-white" placeholder="Email Address" required>
                <input type="password" name="password" class="form-control mb-3 bg-dark text-white" placeholder="Password" required>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success w-100">SUBMIT</button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-link text-white w-100 mt-2" onclick="closeAuth()">Close</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function showAuth(type) { 
            document.getElementById('authOverlay').style.display = 'flex';
            document.getElementById('authForm').action = '/' + type;
        }
        function closeAuth() { document.getElementById('authOverlay').style.display = 'none'; }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
